Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.38,0:00:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火影待你很信賴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種信賴何時建
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.01,0:00:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟婆婆約好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.57,0:00:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在當上火影之前 我絕對不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.44,0:00:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些我很感興趣 真是意味又深長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 火影婆婆將賭注押在了我的身上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.02,0:00:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把約定的信物交給了我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.33,0:00:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如皆人堅信的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓鳴人參戰 才能保護忍者 保護大家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.26,0:00:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我賭鳴人贏 你認為呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.78,0:00:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.99,0:00:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼時候開始打算賭鳴人一次的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.32,0:00:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他擊敗佩因 成為村子英雄的時候嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.38,0:00:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 比那次早很多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.67,0:01:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.59,0:01:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火影根本就是個廢物 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有傻瓜才會做
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.64,0:01:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當著我的面侮辱三代爺爺和第四代的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.02,0:01:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是女人我也不放過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.54,0:01:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要揍扁你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.08,0:01:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.15,0:01:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.56,0:01:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你被我打暈前我想問你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.19,0:01:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼如此執著於火影的稱號
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.80,0:01:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你不同 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.27,0:01:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要得到火影的稱號
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.27,0:01:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…火影是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就來打個賭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.69,0:02:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打賭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.55,0:02:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能在一周內掌握這個忍術
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.70,0:02:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就承認你能夠成為火影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並把這個首飾送給你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.55,0:02:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那場賭局鳴人贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時起 你就將賭注押在他身上了吧  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.32,0:02:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.68,0:02:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老夫第一次見你時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.61,0:02:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只不過賭賭骰子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.20,0:02:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時的我也只有錢可賭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,綱手大人 請等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點啦 靜音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個賭場…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.98,0:04:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 旅店可不會等我們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.05,0:04:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅店才不會跑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.22,0:04:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人 剛剛是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.65,0:04:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與我們無關 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.17,0:04:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大 老大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.08,0:05:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嗎 薩基 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.63,0:05:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是些無聊的事我揍扁你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是無聊的事呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 那個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.85,0:05:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.65,0:05:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是傳說中的… 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.18,0:05:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.71,0:05:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 你不是認識才叫我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是想烘托下氣氛 讓老大更有面子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 我打扁你哦 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.86,0:05:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你偷笑了 老大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然會笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中的肥羊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發財啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.56,0:05:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這些全部換成籌碼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.73,0:06:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你玩得盡興才對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.71,0:06:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請務必盡興 敞開玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全被當成冤大頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有屍體 看來敵人逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.34,0:06:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 那些傢伙將苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.04,0:06:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦真是可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.34,0:06:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(428,35)\fnsimhei\fs22}雲隱這回三個龍套名字的意思是“苦辣甜”，為了延續一貫風格，繼續意譯。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.09,0:06:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之趕快去找甘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.44,0:06:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他應該在附近的旅店等著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能很痛苦 你忍忍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:06:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:07:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 買定離手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.68,0:07:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小 小 小
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.33,0:07:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個一點 小
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.34,0:07:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.23,0:07:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.15,0:07:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝惠顧 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您究竟想幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.10,0:07:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借來的錢已經輸光了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢再借就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.12,0:07:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和誰借啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這家旅館住著一個叫綱手的女人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.64,0:07:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸很大的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們自己去找了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.17,0:07:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 你們是… 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討債的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我仔細搜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 你們是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是從金之國飛來的悍鳥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小妹妹 見過這個大嬸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.27,0:08:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸很大的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.05,0:08:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個漂亮姐姐在其他房間哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.53,0:08:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你們去叫她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 小妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你手裏那個亮晶晶的是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.89,0:08:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫像上那個漂亮姐姐給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說大姐姐遇上些破事 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.59,0:08:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在山裏大發脾氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後在石頭裏發現很多這種亮晶晶的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為拿不下了 所以送了些給我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.77,0:08:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小鬼手上拿的可是金子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來綱手挖到金礦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在討債就虧大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.63,0:09:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多借她錢 多賺利息才是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.31,0:09:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正肯定能討回來的 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.96,0:09:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借她借她 多借點給她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位債主大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.71,0:09:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勞煩你們遠道而來 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.24,0:09:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的賭本也籌好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 去喝酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是詐騙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.93,0:09:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒騙人啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我確實在山上打碎岩石後發現了金子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有這麼點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.50,0:09:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說有很多嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在拓山挖到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(428,35)\fnsimhei\fs22}“拓山”讀音同“很多”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.08,0:09:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.77,0:10:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是甘嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.38,0:10:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷影大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.44,0:10:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧雷影大人引開了敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.86,0:10:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才能平安完成任務
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於拿到杉之國的秘傳忍法帖了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.43,0:10:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在還不能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.05,0:10:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.04,0:10:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.67,0:10:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.02,0:10:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 別小看人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷鼠激震
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.47,0:10:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來 別靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個蟲狀的腫塊在作怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.47,0:11:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腫塊裏注入了會引爆的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.73,0:11:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠吸收附身之人的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要累積到一定量便會爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.73,0:11:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您剛剛說苦最後用了忍術吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.72,0:11:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦使用忍術便會放出大量的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腫塊吸收查克拉後迅速變大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.31,0:11:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會爆炸嗎 甘有救嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.53,0:11:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單憑我的醫療忍術…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕心有餘而力不足
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有個人肯定能救他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且她就在這個鎮上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉的綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:12:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世上沒有比綱手大人更厲害的醫療忍者了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定能…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的很天真呢 甘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但綱手大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別對其他村的忍者如此尊敬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉和雲隱的關係如此之差
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎麼可能願意救我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.45,0:12:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我會讓她救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何也要把綱手帶過來 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.88,0:12:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以 雷影大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.68,0:12:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能為了我去求其他村的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.13,0:12:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要讓她救你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.21,0:12:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您想捨棄作為雷影的榮耀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既不會捨棄 也要救活你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷影大人 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.15,0:12:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您真的比甘還天真
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對部下見死不救算什麼榮耀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.57,0:12:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有什麼資格當雷影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.82,0:12:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛 我不准你死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:13:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要和我一起平安返回
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.33,0:13:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷影大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走 甘 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.36,0:13:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶我去找綱手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.82,0:13:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜音 酒沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.10,0:13:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.09,0:13:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒 酒沒了 拿酒來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.19,0:13:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼點就倒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.71,0:13:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 酒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.07,0:13:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.18,0:13:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 是初代火影 爺爺的項鏈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.69,0:13:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡你了 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要像爺爺一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.69,0:13:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天要繼承火影的名號
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.19,0:13:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為火影是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:13:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次也好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次也好 讓我看看他的笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡村子和同伴們了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想保護他們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.35,0:14:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從妹妹死了之後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份感情就成為了我的支柱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.71,0:14:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人跟我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要成為火影
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為保護大家的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為火影是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個送給你 希望你能收下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.24,0:15:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火影根本就是個廢物 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西當不當才沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只希望你們能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.07,0:15:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你們 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.80,0:15:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想再次見到你們 擁抱你們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.33,0:15:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉傳說中的三忍之一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.25,0:15:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人 我等有事相求
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.25,0:15:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您務必…務必答應我的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.68,0:15:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是雲隱的忍者 甘 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.84,0:15:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託您 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.22,0:15:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用您那卓越的醫療忍術救救我的同伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是雲隱的醫療忍者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.77,0:15:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴受傷 你去醫治不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.82,0:15:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下心有餘而力不足
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.42,0:16:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雲隱的人有什麼資格來求木葉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.27,0:16:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這群想竊取日向白眼的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此事雙方已經解決了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得了便宜還賣乖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不計前嫌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.34,0:16:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了 甘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.69,0:16:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始我就認為你不會乖乖合作的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們雲隱的首領 雷影大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.59,0:16:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真來了一位厲害的大人物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.45,0:16:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不願意我就逼你就範 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.35,0:16:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.60,0:17:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是對誰說話呢 別後悔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.32,0:17:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在後面的空地等你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.89,0:17:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋 竟敢放我鴿子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.96,0:17:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會善罷甘休的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快起來 起來和我戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.34,0:17:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是雲隱的雷影大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.99,0:18:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真來了一位…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.29,0:18:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話你昨天就說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.21,0:18:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別生氣 別生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我們來賭一把吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.43,0:18:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說要來硬的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果扳手腕能贏我就答應你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.38,0:18:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.59,0:18:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我睡著的時候究竟發生了什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.88,0:18:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預備 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.25,0:18:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量竟然在我之上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:18:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.02,0:19:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不能輸 老夫如果在這裏輸掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決不能輸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人竟然輸在力量上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.21,0:19:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.84,0:19:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙一決勝負的瞬間松了手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.91,0:19:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我倆的手之間製造了空隙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.38,0:19:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一瞬間再利用手的加速度扳了回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙並非力量勝過了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.53,0:19:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是以速度取勝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.90,0:19:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可別說我卑鄙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.30,0:19:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會的 我也沒說比力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.73,0:20:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你扳手腕贏了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.67,0:20:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那您願意為辛治療了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.44,0:20:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊請
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 靜音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.80,0:20:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.05,0:20:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.97,0:20:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把最強的醫療忍者綱手大人帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們奪取了杉之國的秘術是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杉之國竟然還有這等高手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方並非杉隱的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.81,0:20:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.60,0:20:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是杉隱雇來的軒轅眾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.50,0:20:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軒轅眾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.38,0:20:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳聞中專門獵殺忍者的軒轅眾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.99,0:21:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在治療中出錯就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.66,0:21:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把經過如實告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.05,0:21:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如您剛才所言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.31,0:21:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這次的任務 就是奪取杉隱的秘術
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.58,0:21:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們仍在搜集秘術嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.45,0:21:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.23,0:21:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪得秘術後 我們分頭行動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.54,0:21:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後由我來說明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.89,0:21:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷影大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.58,0:21:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.19,0:22:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 障眼法嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.28,0:22:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢看不起我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.95,0:22:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.47,0:22:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰 杉隱的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.16,0:22:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是杉隱的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.46,0:22:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒有村子 也沒有主人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.23,0:22:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們受人錢財替人消災
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.67,0:22:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委託我們的是杉隱 請求是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.55,0:22:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將奪取杉隱秘術的人徹底剷除
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.60,0:22:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雇傭忍者之流 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.75,0:22:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.19,0:22:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.89,0:22:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.92,0:22:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們乃遊走於森林的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.09,0:23:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軒轅眾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.94,0:23:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是軒轅眾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.18,0:23:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為獵殺忍者的忍者 軒轅眾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.84,0:23:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷影大人 辛他… 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.13,0:23:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.41,0:23:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 只是一群膽小鬼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.01,0:23:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷影大人 別被敵人挑釁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.63,0:23:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就到平原地帶了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.29,0:23:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雲隱的雷影也沒什麼了不起的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.06,0:23:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.50,0:23:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 別小看人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.55,0:23:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷鼠激震
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.63,0:23:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.89,0:24:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來 別靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.97,0:24:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.96,0:24:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決不會饒恕你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.34,0:24:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 雷影大人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.55,0:24:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和苦都是因為用了忍術身體才出現異常的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.68,0:24:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不能用術啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.95,0:24:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我退後 辛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.08,0:24:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知是不是忌憚全力以赴的我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.66,0:24:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就再也沒露面了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.42,0:24:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這是為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.18,0:24:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是敵人主動攻擊的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.55,0:24:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且苦先生用完術之後就爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.58,0:24:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛先生也想用術
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.64,0:24:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但發現身體的異常後 馬上停止了術
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.37,0:24:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有被炸死
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.75,0:25:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但胸口還是隆起了起爆性查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.53,0:25:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸收術的查克拉 讓他備受煎熬
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.78,0:25:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但為什麼凝聚了強大查克拉的雷影大人反而沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.79,0:25:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.68,0:25:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在目測無法判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.36,0:25:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我在雷影身上感覺到與這個腫塊相同的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.48,0:25:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 我沒感到異常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.90,0:25:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是現在沒感覺而已
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.21,0:25:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個腫塊般的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.18,0:25:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是軒轅眾獨門培育的爆裂蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.72,0:25:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特徵如你所見 
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.65,0:25:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侵入體內 吸收查克拉成長 最終爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.46,0:25:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得一提的是其幼蟲的大小
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.28,0:25:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.06,0:25:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,細菌般的幼蟲 肉眼當然看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.30,0:25:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.60,0:26:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 一開始對話時
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.26,0:26:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就已經中了他們的圈套
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.51,0:26:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次爆炸使幼蟲散播在空氣中
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.62,0:26:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺就會吸入體內
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.22,0:26:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那雷影大人為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.86,0:26:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 為何老夫還沒長出腫塊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.53,0:26:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和辛當時的處境一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.67,0:26:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 別說因為我沒凝聚查克拉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.03,0:26:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛和你扳手腕的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.73,0:26:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消耗了相當多的查克拉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.70,0:26:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雲隱的愣小子 看來毫無長進啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.74,0:26:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.20,0:26:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.57,0:26:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發飆之前聽我解釋啦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.60,0:26:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們忍者發動術之前必須凝聚查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.39,0:26:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查克拉量根據術的不同也大相徑庭
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.68,0:27:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便同一個術 消耗的查克拉量也因人而異
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.67,0:27:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想發動強力的術
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.08,0:27:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然需要相匹配的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.88,0:27:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此查克拉會在一定的時段內聚集在體內
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.34,0:27:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等等
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.89,0:27:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們二位剛才在扳手腕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.75,0:27:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用力量的時候也會消耗查克拉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.71,0:27:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.09,0:27:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但雷影在力量中並未注入查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.95,0:27:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他為了跟力量強大的我抗衡
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.40,0:27:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用速度的優勢贏得了比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.30,0:27:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 速度也需要消耗查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.01,0:27:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將查克拉轉變為速度 
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.43,0:27:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須在一瞬間消耗掉
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.10,0:27:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使爆裂蟲也沒機會吸收這些查克拉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.82,0:27:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我早晚也會變成辛那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.55,0:27:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.98,0:28:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日常生活中總會消耗查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.90,0:28:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摘除蟲子之前 你必須靜養
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.54,0:28:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此說來 你能摘除蟲子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.28,0:28:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 簡單的外科手術就能摘除
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.72,0:28:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜音 準備手術
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.96,0:28:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.43,0:28:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下 我也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.35,0:28:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.68,0:28:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.44,0:28:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這位不知何時會爆炸的部下比較緊急
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.65,0:28:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先給他做手術吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.43,0:28:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題 先救辛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.07,0:28:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下 先給雷影大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.14,0:28:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 雖說是簡單的手術
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.25,0:28:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要將纏繞在複雜經絡系統間的爆裂蟲摘除
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.89,0:28:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也需要相當的醫療知識和經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.60,0:28:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還伴隨著隨時可能爆炸的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.16,0:28:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做手術的人也必須冒生命危險
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.18,0:29:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能由你們任性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.30,0:29:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 綱手 我沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.67,0:29:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先救辛
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.22,0:29:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 不知不覺就…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.68,0:29:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有一個不能先給你做手術的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.33,0:29:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你體內的爆裂蟲肉眼還無法分辨
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.01,0:29:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在它沒長到可以目測之前 我毫無辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.99,0:29:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說如此 也不能掉以輕心
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.65,0:29:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆裂蟲吸收多少查克拉才會變成腫塊並爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.30,0:29:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.34,0:29:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答應我 雷影 
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.65,0:29:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手術要聽我的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.14,0:29:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管發生什麼 都不能輕舉妄動
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.13,0:29:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我答應你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.08,0:29:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你遵守約定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.17,0:30:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.82,0:30:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一只蟲子罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.35,0:30:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.01,0:30:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.71,0:30:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這些 目標就在那片廢墟中
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.53,0:30:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷影的情況如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.10,0:30:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是老樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.80,0:30:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆裂蟲真的吸進去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.69,0:30:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種時機和距離 我不可能失手的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.69,0:30:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.85,0:30:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼爆裂蟲沒成長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.13,0:30:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能弄明白 我們也不用監視了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.33,0:30:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還是一口氣攻進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.35,0:30:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹等真讓人煩躁
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.59,0:30:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別傻了 
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.01,0:30:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個人隨時可能會爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.13,0:30:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去試試啊 只會和他們一起死
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.18,0:31:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了我們的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.39,0:31:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委託人只需要我們平安奪回卷軸
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.85,0:31:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說把取出爆裂蟲當成交換條件
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.25,0:31:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是最簡單的方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.63,0:31:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的生死無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.25,0:31:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把卷軸平安奪回就好
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.61,0:31:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是為了全額的酬金呢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.37,0:31:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且敵人有所增援
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.21,0:31:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要以防萬一
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.56,0:31:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再準備一次爆裂蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.48,0:31:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住全體集中的時機
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.69,0:31:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把消毒液拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.77,0:31:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.72,0:31:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…為了日後的研究 我可以協助你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.09,0:31:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你了 
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.28,0:31:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會用止血術嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.29,0:31:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.27,0:32:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你在那邊做幫手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.62,0:32:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能一邊手術一邊止血 可以節省很多時間
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.69,0:32:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了啊 甘
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.67,0:32:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 不用擔心 
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.85,0:32:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人一定會幫你取出那東西的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.30,0:32:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要開始麻醉了 請放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.94,0:32:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 手術的準備完成了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.17,0:32:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.03,0:32:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛打了麻醉針 一兩分鐘後就能起效了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.67,0:32:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手 辛就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.54,0:32:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜音 你來做
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.66,0:32:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼你不親自出手
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.62,0:32:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是特意請你…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.27,0:32:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 這裏就交給靜音
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.35,0:32:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑什麼讓我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.30,0:33:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認同你是最強的醫療忍者才…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.94,0:33:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心 靜音也是優秀的醫療忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.35,0:33:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且剛剛約好的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.16,0:33:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手術聽我的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.02,0:33:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實如此
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.63,0:33:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果辛有個三長兩短 我不會善罷甘休的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.31,0:33:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心 有問題我會承擔的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.35,0:33:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去地下室睡午覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.07,0:33:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜音 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.73,0:33:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 可以開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.91,0:33:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.59,0:33:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用胸口開口術進行爆裂蟲的摘除手術
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.56,0:33:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,止血術就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.72,0:33:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.84,0:33:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.21,0:33:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是爆裂蟲瞬間長大了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.51,0:33:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.74,0:33:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我可遵守不了不許動的約定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.85,0:34:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了 綱手
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.61,0:34:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了 綱手
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.91,0:34:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血 
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.24,0:34:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.09,0:34:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是恐血症 你怕血嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.74,0:34:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.95,0:34:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你不願替我部下動手術的原因了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.02,0:34:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我去呼吸一下新鮮空氣
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.88,0:35:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這對醫療忍者而言是最致命的毛病啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.27,0:35:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繩樹
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.81,0:35:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斷
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.68,0:35:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫靜音吧 方便回話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.96,0:35:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在動手術
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.62,0:35:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.50,0:36:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果會讓你分心的話 我不勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.79,0:36:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟自來也大蛇丸並稱為木葉三忍的綱手
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.58,0:36:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會患上恐血症呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.61,0:36:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想知道 
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.65,0:36:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人雖然是外村的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.30,0:36:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但對我們醫療忍者而言是個神聖的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.54,0:36:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可綱手大人剛剛的樣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.98,0:36:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.89,0:36:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人有兩位很重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.80,0:36:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一位是她的弟弟繩樹 
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.91,0:36:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在綱手大人送他生日禮物的第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.31,0:36:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死於了第三次忍界大戰
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.46,0:36:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一位是綱手大人的最愛加藤斷
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.63,0:36:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.04,0:36:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.24,0:37:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有很多事要做…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.99,0:37:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說話 斷
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.00,0:37:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能死在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.43,0:37:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 我已經幫你止血了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.67,0:37:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了 你會得救的 斷
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.99,0:37:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.07,0:37:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 別出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.01,0:37:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停下 快停下…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.76,0:37:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我停下…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.11,0:38:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自那天起 綱手大人就陷入了混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.79,0:38:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像苦死在我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.05,0:38:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令我十分動搖一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.21,0:38:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到我竟然將自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.86,0:38:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,押在了醫療忍者生涯已經終結的綱手身上
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.71,0:38:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人的醫療生涯才沒有結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.72,0:38:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆裂蟲摘除手術完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.58,0:38:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷口的恢復就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.01,0:38:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 綱手大人的醫療生涯沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.49,0:38:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會繼承她的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.82,0:38:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 我也會讓綱手大人重新振作
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.34,0:38:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算是為了我過世的叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.77,0:38:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果我還是贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.49,0:38:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後 甘請求的增援趕到
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.41,0:38:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軒轅眾也放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.37,0:38:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是你的運氣好罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.05,0:39:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終你克服了恐血症
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.14,0:39:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這和你賭鳴人會贏有什麼關聯
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.87,0:39:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.46,0:39:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要死…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.34,0:39:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人那堅韌的生命力…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.43,0:39:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…火影是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.26,0:39:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及想成為火影的堅強意志
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.26,0:39:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後讓我決定再賭鳴人一次
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.80,0:39:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我也被牽扯進萬年不中的賭局了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.52,0:39:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今你還說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.27,0:39:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如早點覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.39,0:39:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別傻了 我早就有所覺悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.84,0:40:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自組成忍者聯軍時起    
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.74,0:40:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.21,0:40:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初代火影的項鏈 
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.68,0:40:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我見識瞧一瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.11,0:40:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.51,0:40:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發動九尾的時候 似乎被我弄壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.19,0:40:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是很重要的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.36,0:40:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 因為我和婆婆的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.97,0:40:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都有一份不變的約定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.23,0:40:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 大家一定都在等著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.21,0:42:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,你們享受著殺戮
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.58,0:42:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,同為忍者 這點讓人生厭
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.02,0:42:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,少裝腔作勢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.57,0:42:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,你這把刀是從誰手上弄到的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.59,0:42:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,那是我們忍刀七人眾的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.05,0:42:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,居然為外人所用 真不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.30,0:42:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,對付兩個這樣的對手 
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.77,0:42:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,確實很吃力
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.97,0:42:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,下集 火影忍者疾風傳
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.77,0:42:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,威脅 甚八.串丸組合
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.69,0:42:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,看來遇到危機了啊 朋友
